lass='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/su-khac-biet-cua-cac-cong-nghe-cam-ung-dang-co-tren-thi-truong\/#cam_ung_dien_tro_resistive_touchscreen\" >C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u1edf (Resistive Touchscreen)<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/su-khac-biet-cua-cac-cong-nghe-cam-ung-dang-co-tren-thi-truong\/#cam_ung_dien_dung_capacitive_touchscreen\" >C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec7n dung (Capacitive Touchscreen)<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/su-khac-biet-cua-cac-cong-nghe-cam-ung-dang-co-tren-thi-truong\/#cam_ung_hong_ngoai_infrared_touchscreen\" >C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng h\u1ed3ng ngo\u1ea1i (Infrared Touchscreen)<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/su-khac-biet-cua-cac-cong-nghe-cam-ung-dang-co-tren-thi-truong\/#cam_ung_song_am_be_mat_surface_acoustic_wave_%e2%80%93_saw\" >C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng s\u00f3ng \u00e2m b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t (Surface Acoustic Wave &#8211; SAW)<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/su-khac-biet-cua-cac-cong-nghe-cam-ung-dang-co-tren-thi-truong\/#cam_ung_quang_hoc_optical_touchscreen\" >C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng quang h\u1ecdc (Optical Touchscreen)<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/su-khac-biet-cua-cac-cong-nghe-cam-ung-dang-co-tren-thi-truong\/#ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta. T\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb th\u00f4ng minh, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang ta t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cam_ung_dien_tro_resistive_touchscreen\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\"><strong>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u1edf (Resistive Touchscreen)<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15992\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Resistive-Touch.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"549\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Resistive-Touch.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Resistive-Touch-656x400.webp 656w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Resistive-Touch-768x468.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Resistive-Touch-600x366.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u1edf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean hai l\u1edbp v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u d\u1eabn \u0111i\u1ec7n (th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 kim lo\u1ea1i m\u1ecfng) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u0103n c\u00e1ch b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp kh\u00f4ng d\u1eabn \u0111i\u1ec7n. Khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, hai l\u1edbp n\u00e0y \u00e9p v\u00e0o nhau, t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh d\u00f2ng \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111i qua v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1m. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i d\u00f2ng \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u00e0o, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ng\u00f3n tay, b\u00fat c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng, ho\u1eb7c ngay c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi g\u0103ng tay.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh r\u1ebb h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng kh\u00e1c.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 nh\u1ea1y kh\u00f4ng cao, c\u1ea7n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m.<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb k\u00e9m h\u01a1n, do c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u.<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m (multi-touch).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u1edf th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb nh\u01b0 m\u00e1y r\u00fat ti\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng (ATM), h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng kiosk b\u00e1n l\u1ebb, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eddi c\u0169.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cam_ung_dien_dung_capacitive_touchscreen\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\"><strong>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec7n dung (Capacitive Touchscreen)<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15996\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/capacitive-touch-screen.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/capacitive-touch-screen.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/capacitive-touch-screen-711x400.webp 711w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/capacitive-touch-screen-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/capacitive-touch-screen-600x337.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec7n dung ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u00f2ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eeb c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u t\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ean trong. Khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eeb c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec7n dung t\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m, v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1m d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 nh\u1ea1y cao, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m nh\u1eb9 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m, gi\u00fap tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n (v\u00ed d\u1ee5: zoom, k\u00e9o, vu\u1ed1t).<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb t\u1ed1t, v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng khi \u0111eo g\u0103ng tay ho\u1eb7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng d\u1eabn \u0111i\u1ec7n.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u1edf.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec7n dung l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb th\u00f4ng minh nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, laptop, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed gia d\u1ee5ng th\u00f4ng minh.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cam_ung_hong_ngoai_infrared_touchscreen\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\"><strong>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng h\u1ed3ng ngo\u1ea1i (Infrared Touchscreen)<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15993\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/infrared-touch-screen-technology.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"450\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/infrared-touch-screen-technology.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/infrared-touch-screen-technology-800x400.webp 800w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/infrared-touch-screen-technology-768x384.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/infrared-touch-screen-technology-600x300.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng h\u1ed3ng ngo\u1ea1i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c tia h\u1ed3ng ngo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed d\u1ecdc theo c\u1ea1nh m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh. Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, tay c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1eaft ngang tia h\u1ed3ng ngo\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1m b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch theo d\u00f5i s\u1ef1 gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tia n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n cao, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<li>Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ng\u00f3n tay.<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, khi\u1ebfn vi\u1ec1n m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh d\u00e0y h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<li>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5u b\u1edfi c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n s\u00e1ng m\u1ea1nh, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng cao.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng h\u1ed3ng ngo\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c l\u1edbn, c\u00e1c kiosk th\u00f4ng tin, v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n trong nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cam_ung_song_am_be_mat_surface_acoustic_wave_%e2%80%93_saw\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\"><strong>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng s\u00f3ng \u00e2m b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t (Surface Acoustic Wave &#8211; SAW)<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15994\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Surface-Acoustic-Wave-SAW.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"386\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Surface-Acoustic-Wave-SAW.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Surface-Acoustic-Wave-SAW-800x343.webp 800w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Surface-Acoustic-Wave-SAW-768x329.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Surface-Acoustic-Wave-SAW-600x257.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng s\u00f3ng \u00e2m b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u00f3ng \u00e2m truy\u1ec1n d\u1ecdc theo b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh. Khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, c\u00e1c s\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1m, v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ecda \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cao, nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf.<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u1ed1t, do m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh trong su\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb che b\u1edfi c\u00e1c l\u1edbp c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n ho\u1eb7c \u1ea9m \u01b0\u1edbt, v\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ea1t b\u1ee5i ho\u1eb7c n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00f3ng \u00e2m.<\/li>\n<li>D\u1ec5 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 v\u1eadt l\u00fd nh\u01b0 tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c va \u0111\u1eadp m\u1ea1nh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng s\u00f3ng \u00e2m b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng kiosk v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c l\u1edbn.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cam_ung_quang_hoc_optical_touchscreen\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\"><strong>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng quang h\u1ecdc (Optical Touchscreen)<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15995\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Optical-Touchscreen.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"477\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Optical-Touchscreen.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Optical-Touchscreen-755x400.webp 755w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Optical-Touchscreen-768x407.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Optical-Touchscreen-600x318.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng quang h\u1ecdc ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng camera ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn quang h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn d\u1ecdc theo c\u1ea1nh m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh. Khi c\u00f3 v\u1eadt th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1m.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 nh\u1ea1y cao, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1eadt l\u00fd tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<li>Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh b\u1ecb tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn, do \u0111\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng kh\u00e1c.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng quang h\u1ecdc th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, kiosk th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket_luan\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\"><strong>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u01b0u nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m ri\u00eang, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1c nhau trong \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p. C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec7n dung l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn cho c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i v\u00e0 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1ea1y cao v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng h\u1ed3ng ngo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 quang h\u1ecdc l\u1ea1i th\u00edch h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n cho c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n. Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c.<\/p>\n<div id=\"eJOY__extension_root\" class=\"eJOY__extension_root_class\" style=\"all: unset;\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta. T\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb th\u00f4ng minh, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang ta t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":15998,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-15989","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15989","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15989"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15989\/revisions"}],"predecesso